description: TEHRAN – Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Ali Khamenei on Thursday prayed over the coffins of seven Islamic Revolution Guards Corps servicepersons who were martyred in Israeli air strikes on the consular building of the Iranian embassy in Syria on April 1.
title: Ayatollah Khamenei prays over coffins of military advisors assassinated in Syria

description: TEHRAN – In a statement on Thursday, the government of Pakistan condemned the attacks by the terrorist Jaish al-Adl group in the cities of Rask and Chabahar in the border province of Sistan-Baluchestan in southeast Iran.
title: Pakistan condemns terrorist attack in Iran’s border region

description: TEHRAN - The annual observance of International Quds Day by millions of Muslims worldwide serves as a significant platform to express solidarity with the Palestinian cause. Particularly this year, amidst the ongoing conflict in Gaza, a surge in global participation is anticipated, as the brutal realities of the Israeli regime's actions have galvanized international attention.
title: Gaza is an awakening for the world

description: TEHRAN- In recent weeks, there has been a notable rise in official opposition from Western governments towards the policies of the occupying Israeli regime concerning the Gaza Strip. As a result, various restrictions have been placed on arms and financial aid to the Tel Aviv regime, particularly targeting financial transactions and support for border settlements with Gaza and newly established settlements on the West Bank.
title: The West facing challenges in the Gaza conflict

description: TEHRAN - 18 terrorists and armed criminals have been killed in the southeastern border province of Sistan-Baluchestan, the Islamic Revolution Guards Corps (IRGC) said in a statement on Thursday.
title: 18 terrorists killed in southeast Iran

description: TEHRAN – The occupied city of al-Quds holds a sacred place in the hearts of Muslims worldwide, embodying resilience, faith, and struggle for liberation. Similarly, for the Islamic Republic of Iran, Al-Quds transcends mere geography; it emerges as a spiritual and ideological bedrock intricately entwined with the nation's essence and aspirations.
title: Embracing spirit of Quds Day: Iran's advocacy for Palestinian cause

description: TEHRAN- Quds Day unites people globally in solidarity with Gaza, amplifying voices and highlighting Palestinian struggles for justice and freedom.
title: Quds Day: Gaza's message loud and clear

description: TEHRAN - The Leader of the Islamic Revolution, Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei, has consistently highlighted the importance of unity among Muslims in supporting Palestine in his addresses on the International Quds Day.
title: Ayatollah Khamenei's perspective on Quds Day: ‘Empowering Palestinian Cause’

description: TEHRAN- The last Friday of the holy month of Ramadan marks International Quds Day, a day dedicated to showing solidarity with the Palestinian people and their struggle against Israeli occupation.
title: Imam Khomeini's enduring legacy: International Quds Day unites millions in support of Palestine

description: TEHRAN- Iranian President Ebrahim Raisi has underscored the significance of bilateral and regional collaboration with Iraq, highlighting the alignment between Tehran and Baghdad against the Israeli regime.
title: Iran prioritizes bilateral, regional cooperation with Iraq, says Raisi

description: TEHRAN – Iran’s men’s football team remained unchanged in latest FIFA ranking released on Thursday.
title: Iran still 20th in FIFA ranking
